<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Ya Ubangijinmu Yesu,
 Tsare mu da daren nan.
 Kada kome ya same mu,
 Rufe mu da hannunka.

[V2]
 Tun da farkon hasken safe
 Kana nan tare da mu.
 Ko da duhu ya rufe mu,
 Kana wurin har yanzu.</lyrics>
<title>Ya Ubangijinmu Yesu, Tsare Mu da Daren Nan LW26</title>
<hymn_number>26</hymn_number>
</song>